                        </div>
                        <div class="color pa">
                            <img src="imgs/cerberus puppy cmyk2_Mesa de trabajo 1.jpg" alt="lc">
                            <h3>Color</h3>
                            <p class="txtlineart">Then I look for the right color palette for what the client is looking for, or I use the one that has been given to me
                            if there is already an existing one.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="detalles pa">
                            <img src="imgs/cerberus puppy terminado 1.jpg" alt="lineart cerberus poppy">
